---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About me">
  <h1><span class="prompt">$</span> cat about.txt</h1>

  <div class="content">
    <p>
    Hi, I'm Machine Learning Eng. at the Kempner Institue. I love talking about ML, optimization and books.
    In this blog I share my thoughts and ideas about these topics. 
    </p>

    <h2>Background</h2>
    <p>
    I have experience in  machine learning, natural language processing and HPC. Plus, I am interested in political philosophy and russian literature!
    </p>

    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Machine Learning</li>
      <li>Explainable AI</li>
      <li>GPU optimization</li>
      <li>ML for protein biology</li>
      <li>Political philosophy</li>
      <li>Russian Literature</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      You can find me on <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a> 
      or reach out via email.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prompt {
    color: var(--accent-green);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
</style>
